# LoomHub

LoomHub is the hosted hub and collaboration layer for Loom. It is separate from the core Loom system and lives in its own repository.

Use LoomHub when you want:

- hosted hub infrastructure
- web-based loom browsing
- weave requests, reviews, and collaboration
- shared send/receive workflows for teams

This VitePress site focuses on Loom itself. For LoomHub implementation and product design, use the sibling repository at `/Users/flakerim/LoomProject/loomhub`.
